"访问电子邮件队列。未发送的邮件显示为绿松石色，已发送的邮件显示为灰色。"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/faq.rst:27
msgid "Common error messages"
msgstr "常见错误消息"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/faq.rst:32
